                     <interp inst="t18201206-121-person1166" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I found the prisoner at the watch-house.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw it laying down - I took it up, and put it down again.</p>
               <p>
